ogging(level=logging.INFO)`:\n102:   - [ ] Configure root logger with format\n103:   - [ ] Return logger instance\n104: \n105: ### T010: High-level Code Interpreter client\n106: - [ ] Create `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n107: - [ ] Implement `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__(router_url, workload_manager_url=None, name=None, namespace=\"default\", session_id=None, ttl=3600, timeout=120)`:\n108:   - [ ] Validate `router_url` is provided (arg or `ROUTER_URL` env)\n109:   - [ ] Store config\n110:   - [ ] If `session_id` not provided:\n111:     - [ ] Create `ControlPlaneClient`\n112:     - [ ] Call `create_session()`\n113:     - [ ] Handle failure: delete session, re-raise\n114:   - [ ] Call `_init_data_plane()`\n115: - [ ] Implement `_init_data_plane()`:\n116:   - [ ] Create `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` with `session_id`\n117: - [ ] Implement context manager protocol:\n118:   - [ ] `__enter__()`: return `self`\n119:   - [ ] `__exit__(exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb)`: call `stop()`\n120: - [ ] Implement `stop()`:\n121:   - [ ] Close data plane session\n122:   - [ ] If created session: call `delete_session()`\n123:   - [ ] Close control plane session\n124: - [ ] Implement `execute_command(command, timeout=None) -> dict`: delegate to data plane\n125: - [ ] Implement `run_code(code, language=\"python\") -> dict`:\n126:   - [ ] Write timestamped `.py` file\n127:   - [ ] Execute `python3 <file>`\n128: - [ ] Implement `write_file(path, content)`: delegate to data plane\n129: - [ ] Implement `upload_file(local_path, remote_path)`: delegate to data plane\n130: - [ ] Implement `download_file(remote_path, local_path)`: delegate to data plane\n131: - [ ] Implement `list_files(path) -> list`: delegate to data plane\n132: \n133: ### T011: High-level Agent Runtime client\n134: - [ ] Create `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n135: - [ ] Implement `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__(router_url, namespace, agent_name, session_id=None, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0)`:\n136:   