ile Targets\n1090: \n1091: **File**: `Makefile`\n1092: \n1093: ```makefile\n1094: # Code generation\n1095: .PHONY: gen-client\n1096: gen-client:\n1097: \t@echo \"Generating client-go code...\"\n1098: \t@bash hack/update-codegen.sh\n1099: \t@go mod tidy\n1100: \n1101: .PHONY: gen-client-verify\n1102: gen-client-verify:\n1103: \t@echo \"Verifying client-go code is up-to-date...\"\n1104: \t@bash hack/verify-codegen.sh\n1105: ```\n1106: \n1107: ### Generated Code Structure\n1108: \n1109: | Directory | Purpose | Generator |\n1110: |-----------|---------|-----------|\n1111: | `clientset/versioned/` | ClientSet and typed clients | client-gen |\n1112: | `informers/externalversions/` | Informers for event watching | informer-gen |\n1113: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/` | Listers for read-only access | lister-gen |\n1114: \n1115: ## Integration Points\n1116: \n1117: ### With Controller Manager\n1118: \n1119: The Controller Manager uses the generated client-go to:\n1120: 1. Watch AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs for changes\n1121: 2. Reconcile resources based on spec changes\n1122: 3. Update status subresource with observed state\n1123: 4. Handle finalizers and cleanup\n1124: \n1125: ```go\n1126: // Example usage in controller\n1127: import (\n1128:     clientset \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n1129:     runtimev1alpha1 \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n1130: )\n1131: \n1132: type AgentRuntimeReconciler struct {\n1133:     client clientset.Interface\n1134:     informer cache.SharedIndexInformer\n1135: }\n1136: \n1137: func (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, key string) error {\n1138:     namespace, name, err := cache.SplitMetaNamespaceKey(key)\n1139:     if err != nil {\n1140:         return err\n1141:     }\n1142: \n1143:     agentRuntime, err := r.client.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(namespace).Get(ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n1144:     if errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n1145:         