`k8s.io/code-generator` | v0.28.0 | Generate client-go code |\n1213: | `go` | 1.21+ | Build and test |\n1214: \n1215: ## Documentation\n1216: \n1217: ### Package Documentation\n1218: \n1219: **File**: `README.md`\n1220: \n1221: ```markdown\n1222: # AgentCube client-go\n1223: \n1224: Type-safe Kubernetes client library for AgentCube custom resources.\n1225: \n1226: ## Installation\n1227: \n1228: ```bash\n1229: go get github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\n1230: ```\n1231: \n1232: ## Usage\n1233: \n1234: ### Create ClientSet\n1235: \n1236: ```go\n1237: import (\n1238:     \"k8s.io/client-go/tools/clientcmd\"\n1239:     clientset \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n1240: )\n1241: \n1242: config, err := clientcmd.BuildConfigFromFlags(\"\", kubeconfig)\n1243: if err != nil {\n1244:     panic(err)\n1245: }\n1246: \n1247: client, err := clientset.NewForConfig(config)\n1248: if err != nil {\n1249:     panic(err)\n1250: }\n1251: ```\n1252: \n1253: ### Create AgentRuntime\n1254: \n1255: ```go\n1256: agentRuntime := &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n1257:     ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n1258:         Name:      \"my-agent\",\n1259:         Namespace: \"default\",\n1260:     },\n1261:     Spec: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n1262:         MaxSessionDuration: \"8h\",\n1263:         SessionTimeout:     \"15m\",\n1264:         TargetPort: []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort{\n1265:             {Port: 8080, Protocol: \"HTTP\"},\n1266:         },\n1267:     },\n1268: }\n1269: \n1270: created, err := client.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(ctx, agentRuntime, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n1271: if err != nil {\n1272:     panic(err)\n1273: }\n1274: ```\n1275: \n1276: ### Use Informers\n1277: \n1278: ```go\n1279: factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(client, time.Minute)\n1280: informer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()\n1281: \n1282: informer.AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n1283:     AddFunc: func(obj interface{}) {\n1284:         agentRuntime := obj.(*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n1285:         fmt.Printf(\"AgentRuntime %s added\\n\", agentRuntime.Name)\n1286:     },\n1287:     UpdateFunc: func(oldObj, newObj interface{}) {\n1288:         oldRuntime := oldObj.(*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n1289:         newRuntime := newObj.(*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n1290:         if oldRuntime.ResourceVersion != newRuntime.ResourceVersion {\n1291:             fmt.Printf(\"AgentRuntime %s updated\\n\", newRuntime.Name)\n1292:         }\n1293:     },\n1294:     DeleteFunc: func(obj interface{}) {\n1295:         agentRuntime := obj.(*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n1296:         fmt.Printf(\"AgentRuntime %s deleted\\n\", agentRuntime.Name)\n1297:     },\n1298: })\n1299: \n1300: stopCh := make(chan struct{})\n\n(Output capped at 50 KB. Showing lines 1-1300. Use offset=1301 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Design\n\n## AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n**Module**: `client-go`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: L\n**Purpose**: Generate a type-safe Kubernetes client-go library for AgentCube custom resources (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter), providing typed API access with CRUD operations, Watch mechanism, and Informer pattern support.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/\n│   └── versioned/\n│       ├── clientset.go                    # Clientset, Interface, constructors\n│       ├── doc.go                          # Package documentation\n│       ├── scheme/","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","time":{"start":1775887438588,"end":1775887438607}}}}
