teOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n37:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n38:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n39:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n40:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n41: }\n42: ```\n43: \n44: #### AgentRuntime Methods\n45: \n46: **Create**\n47: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n48: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n49: - **Description**: Create a new AgentRuntime resource\n50: \n51: **Update**\n52: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n53: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n54: - **Description**: Update an existing AgentRuntime resource\n55: \n56: **UpdateStatus**\n57: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n58: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n59: - **Description**: Update the status subresource of an AgentRuntime\n60: \n61: **Delete**\n62: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n63: - **Returns**: `error`\n64: - **Description**: Delete an AgentRuntime resource by name\n65: \n66: **Get**\n67: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n68: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n69: - **Description**: Get an AgentRuntime resource by name\n70: \n71: **List**\n72: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n73: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList`, `error`\n74: - **Description**: List AgentRuntime resources\n75: \n76: **Watch**\n77: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n78: - **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n79: - **Description**: Watch for AgentRuntime resource changes\n80: \n81: **Patch**\n82: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n83: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n84: - **Description**: Patch an AgentRuntime resource\n85: \n86: ### CodeInterpreter Client\n87: \n88: #### CodeInterpreterInterface\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n92:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n93:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n94:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n95:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n96:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n97:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n98:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n99:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n100:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: #### CodeInterpreter Methods\n105: \n106: **Create**\n107: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.CreateOp