meInformer interface {\n152:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n153:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n154: }\n155: ```\n156: \n157: #### CodeInterpreterInformer\n158: \n159: ```go\n160: type CodeInterpreterInformer interface {\n161:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n162:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n163: }\n164: ```\n165: \n166: ### Lister\n167: \n168: #### AgentRuntimeLister\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n172:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n173:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n174:     AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n175: }\n176: ```\n177: \n178: #### CodeInterpreterLister\n179: \n180: ```go\n181: type CodeInterpreterLister interface {\n182:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n183:     CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n184:     CodeInterpreterListerExpansion\n185: }\n186: ```\n187: \n188: ## Common Types\n189: \n190: ### API Verbs\n191: \n192: Common verbs for API operations:\n193: - `create` - Create a resource\n194: - `update` - Update a resource\n195: - `delete` - Delete a resource\n196: - `get` - Get a single resource\n197: - `list` - List multiple resources\n198: - `watch` - Watch for resource changes\n199: - `patch` - Patch a resource\n200: \n201: ### Context\n202: \n203: All client methods accept a `context.Context` for:\n204: - Request cancellation\n205: - Timeout control\n206: - Request-scoped values\n207: \n208: ### Error Handling\n209: \n210: All client methods return `error` for:\n211: - Network errors\n212: - API errors\n213: - Validation errors\n214: - Authentication/authorization errors\n215: \n216: ## Best Practices\n217: \n218: - Always provide context to client methods\n219: - Use proper error handling\n220: - Implement retry logic for transient failures\n221: - Use Listers for read-only operations